Template for an image with buttons. 1-3 are supported
(maybe more) and they can be web_urls or postbacks. Again
for button payload, this is instruction that comes back
from the agent, not that goes out.
<!--==============================-->

<response>
    <image_buttons>
        <url>__fbMediaURL</url>
        <buttons>
            <type>web_url</type>
            <url>__urlOnClick</url>
            <title>__buttonText</title>
        </buttons>
        <buttons>
            <type>postback</type>
            <title>__buttonText</title>
            <payload>__instructionOnClick</payload>
        </buttons>
    </image_buttons>
</response>